      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-14T01:53:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I agree that we need a way to accurately capture the specific flash layout for partial updates and validation. I have replied in the main commit thread to discuss whether we should follow the CPLD enum pattern.",
